<h3>
 Question 1
</h3>
<co-content>
 <p>
  <strong>
   ***This is NOT a graded quiz, this is to clarify your understanding of the Peer Review Critique Assignment. ***
  </strong>
 </p>
 <p>
  To test your capability to critique an interface design using the course design principles, you will produce a critique of part of the MetroTransit.org public transit route finder interface, presented through the linked video here:
 </p>
 <p>
 </p>
 <asset assettype="video" extension="mp4" id="fwLt-VUDEeaztg6Pg6w09w" name="metro-transit">
 </asset>
 <p>
  Once you have submitted your critique, please compare your critique with ours (our critique will only be visible AFTER you submit your critique ) to verify your understanding of what is expected in this upcoming assignment.
 </p>
 <p>
  <strong>
   If you are satisfied with your response, please move on to the "Peer Review: Interface Critique" .
  </strong>
 </p>
</co-content>
